Interface DataRow

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
Data, MetaData
public interface DataRow
extends java.io.Serializable

Specifies constants for the data row and element positions in the data array. Provides the basic structure and names of the data and the data array.
